                <h1>Remember the Alamo: A Symbol of Courage and Sacrifice</h1>
                <p>Remember the Alamo is a pivotal moment in American history, symbolizing courage and sacrifice. In 1836, a group of Texan defenders fought valiantly against overwhelming Mexican forces at the Alamo Mission. Despite their ultimate defeat, their bravery inspired the Texan revolution, leading to independence from Mexico and a lasting legacy of heroism.</p>
